%section
  %h4 Comparison Rules
  %ul
    %li
      Strings must be
      %strong single-quoted
      inside expressions:
      %code status = 'active'
    %li
      Use
      %code =
      or
      %code ==
      for equality,
      %code !=
      or
      %code <>
      for inequality.
    %li
      Boolean literals:
      %code true
      and
      %code false
      (case-insensitive).
    %li
      String comparison is
      %strong case-insensitive.
    %li
      %code nil
      and empty string are falsy in boolean context.
